  "short_description": "Elevate your desktop with Infinite Widgets, the ultimate tool for creating and sharing custom widgets. Monitor system performance, hardware temperatures, control media, create dock/taskbar widgets, and more with the built-in editor and our Lua and JavaScript implementation.",
