  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/ae9726f97abfcabfce6e1a40c8d4bda9.avif?t=1758116753\" width=616 height=240 /></span><strong>Elevate your desktop with Infinite Widgets, the ultimate software for creating custom widgets that display everything you need</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With Infinite Widgets create, share or download widgets that enhance your desktop user experience</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/d82b64d717908cdf39e76a6e6bd62578.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Software developer ?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With our built-in renderer and Lua support, you can create unique widgets tailored to your specific needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More of a Web developer? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our JavaScript integration allows you to create web-based widgets with the same depth as our Lua implementation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Communication between Lua and JavaScript is possible, making it easy to build complex, interactive widgets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Not a developer ?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our editor allows you to create widgets without coding !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For those interested, learning to code with Infinite Widgets can be a fun and rewarding experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/c8f2ee581b10a95d590ff39a07279561.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Real-Time Monitoring</strong>: Show detailed system performance information<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/a7869c0a46194edc1b29e7606f98568b.avif?t=1758116753\" width=480 height=336 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Media Support</strong>: Display and control the music playing on your system<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/595fe8eaf19f516342cb5a92540c6836.avif?t=1758116753\" width=299 height=384 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Window Docking</strong>: Create widgets with reserved monitor work areas<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/f375e4b05672500a623f5462d04e04d1.avif?t=1758116753\" width=415 height=611 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Dock and Taskbar</strong>: Create your own Windows Dock or Taskbar widget<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/0c1d385defc0e0985669ab0562588efa.avif?t=1758116753\" width=406 height=115 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Steam Integration</strong>: Launch Steam games, view game thumbnails, and access your most recent and most played games<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/23297a33e5ccae087975860379628e0f.avif?t=1758116753\" width=444 height=390 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Sticked or Not</strong>: Create desktop sticked widgets or on top of everything widgets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Multiple views </strong>: Run multiple instances of the same widget simultaneously</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Storage</strong>: Widgets can save and retrieve custom data</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Looking for more? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a variety of tools to create your own unique widgets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/a558c932e873fcd82db701bf64c6cc95.avif?t=1758116753\" width=404 height=403 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/5bc98925a827850812b1d5d51ce6df08.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Concerned about performances ?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinite Widgets maintains very low processor usage, ensuring it won't interfere with your computer's performance or gaming experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/58e5ac9106f9a50fec6c7359e235694e.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Need help getting started?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We offer examples widgets along with a built-in comprehensive documentation on using our Lua and JavaScript implementations, as well as key elements of the editor, ensuring you have all the information you need to make the most of Infinite Widgets !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With Infinite Widgets, your desktop will be both functional and stylish.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/ae9726f97abfcabfce6e1a40c8d4bda9.avif?t=1758116753\" width=616 height=240 /></span><strong>Elevate your desktop with Infinite Widgets, the ultimate software for creating custom widgets that display everything you need</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With Infinite Widgets create, share or download widgets that enhance your desktop user experience</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/d82b64d717908cdf39e76a6e6bd62578.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Software developer ?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With our built-in renderer and Lua support, you can create unique widgets tailored to your specific needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More of a Web developer? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our JavaScript integration allows you to create web-based widgets with the same depth as our Lua implementation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Communication between Lua and JavaScript is possible, making it easy to build complex, interactive widgets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Not a developer ?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our editor allows you to create widgets without coding !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For those interested, learning to code with Infinite Widgets can be a fun and rewarding experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/c8f2ee581b10a95d590ff39a07279561.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Real-Time Monitoring</strong>: Show detailed system performance information<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/a7869c0a46194edc1b29e7606f98568b.avif?t=1758116753\" width=480 height=336 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Media Support</strong>: Display and control the music playing on your system<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/595fe8eaf19f516342cb5a92540c6836.avif?t=1758116753\" width=299 height=384 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Window Docking</strong>: Create widgets with reserved monitor work areas<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/f375e4b05672500a623f5462d04e04d1.avif?t=1758116753\" width=415 height=611 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Dock and Taskbar</strong>: Create your own Windows Dock or Taskbar widget<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/0c1d385defc0e0985669ab0562588efa.avif?t=1758116753\" width=406 height=115 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Steam Integration</strong>: Launch Steam games, view game thumbnails, and access your most recent and most played games<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/23297a33e5ccae087975860379628e0f.avif?t=1758116753\" width=444 height=390 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Sticked or Not</strong>: Create desktop sticked widgets or on top of everything widgets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Multiple views </strong>: Run multiple instances of the same widget simultaneously</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Storage</strong>: Widgets can save and retrieve custom data</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Looking for more? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a variety of tools to create your own unique widgets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/a558c932e873fcd82db701bf64c6cc95.avif?t=1758116753\" width=404 height=403 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/5bc98925a827850812b1d5d51ce6df08.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Concerned about performances ?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinite Widgets maintains very low processor usage, ensuring it won't interfere with your computer's performance or gaming experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/58e5ac9106f9a50fec6c7359e235694e.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Need help getting started?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We offer examples widgets along with a built-in comprehensive documentation on using our Lua and JavaScript implementations, as well as key elements of the editor, ensuring you have all the information you need to make the most of Infinite Widgets !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With Infinite Widgets, your desktop will be both functional and stylish.</p>",
